{"tid":2051053,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局夥銀行為應屆大學畢業生提供300個短期職位","createTime":"2020-06-04T13:17:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T23:07:55.000Z","uid":101341,"like":10,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9c0bbfcd05310ac796d75b44be2d6116a8c82466","tid":2051053,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T13:17:32.000Z","msg":"金融管理局宣布將與銀行業界合作，推出「銀行業人才起動計劃」，為應屆本地大學本科畢業生提供約300個為期6個月的工作機會。計劃於6月中起接受報名，獲聘的畢業生9月開始工作，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">月薪為12,000元</span>。為鼓勵業界參與計劃，金管局會資助其中最多一半的薪金。<br />\n<br />\n此外，金管局會於計劃期間安排及資助受聘的畢業生接受專業培訓，例如讓這批職場新人參加金融相關的講座，以及一些專業培訓課程。局方期望相關安排，能夠幫助畢業生增進銀行業的專業知識，為將來投身金融業時作更好的準備。"},{"pid":"92855db5cb63e50e7503d15e7d382992eb41ab16","tid":2051053,"uid":83646,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T13:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狗也不"},{"pid":"508dd004bc327f9f3fa946fa89848b347c9410ba","tid":2051053,"uid":214502,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T13:19:41.000Z","msg":"哇 多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8caa5cfcabcc228d354ca37f03c99d5bf1377e8e","tid":2051053,"uid":120627,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T13:20:15.000Z","msg":"加多5000 ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4fe54e669da1f2de26489d0610ad901ea34f35f","tid":2051053,"uid":289708,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T13:20:24.000Z","msg":"12000仲要得六個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab40c73fd4e72b5e67312bdb6c73f90086101c45","tid":2051053,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8caa5cfcabcc228d354ca37f03c99d5bf1377e8e","tid":2051053,"uid":120627,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T13:20:15.000Z","msg":"加多5000 ok?<img src=\"/assets